---
layout: layouts/inner.njk
title: Careers
permalink: /careers/
eyebrow:
  en: Careers
  vi: Tuyển dụng
  zh: 招聘
heading:
  en: Grow with Nam Viet.
  vi: Cùng Nam Việt phát triển.
  zh: 与南越共同成长。
lead:
  en: Join teams across manufacturing, logistics, sustainability and corporate functions.
  vi: Gia nhập các đội ngũ sản xuất, logistics, bền vững và khối văn phòng.
  zh: 加入生产、物流、可持续发展与企业职能部门。
---

<section class="page-section">
  <h2>
    <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.openRoles }}</span>
    <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.openRoles }}</span>
    <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.openRoles }}</span>
  </h2>

  <div class="career-list">
    {% for job in careers %}
    <article class="career-card" id="{{ job.id }}">
      <div>
        <h3>
          <span class="lang en">{{ job.title.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ job.title.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ job.title.zh }}</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="career-card__meta">
          <span class="lang en">{{ job.department.en }} · {{ job.location.en }} · {{ job.type.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ job.department.vi }} · {{ job.location.vi }} · {{ job.type.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ job.department.zh }} · {{ job.location.zh }} · {{ job.type.zh }}</span>
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="lang en">{{ job.summary.en }}</span>
          <span class="lang vi">{{ job.summary.vi }}</span>
          <span class="lang zh">{{ job.summary.zh }}</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn--small btn--solid" href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}?type=careers&amp;role={{ job.id }}">
        <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.applyNow }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.applyNow }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.applyNow }}</span>
      </a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
